  "prompt": "How can I get the mark-sheet transcripts from Jadavpur University?",
  "response": "To obtain your mark-sheet transcripts from Jadavpur University, follow these steps:\n\n### 1. **Visit the University Website**\n   - Go to the official Jadavpur University website: [https://www.jaduniv.edu.in/](https://www.jaduniv.edu.in/).\n   - Look for the **\"Examination\"** or **\"Academics\"** section, where transcript-related information is usually provided.\n\n### 2. **Check the Transcript Application Process**\n   - Some universities provide detailed instructions or downloadable forms on their website. If available, download the **Transcript Application Form**.\n   - If the form is not available online, you may need to visit the university in person.\n\n### 3. **Prepare Required Documents**\n   - Usually, the following documents are required:\n     - Printed and filled **Transcript Application Form**.\n     - Photocopies of your **mark sheets** and **degree certificate**.\n     - A valid **ID proof** (e.g., Aadhar card, passport, or driver's license).\n     - **Passport-sized photographs** (as specified by the university).\n     - **Demand Draft (DD)** or payment confirmation for the transcript fee (if applicable).\n\n### 4. **Submit Your Application**\n   - Submit the application form and required documents to the **Examination Section** or the **Controller of Examinations Office** at Jadavpur University.\n   - If you are unable to visit in person, check if the university allows sending the application via post or through an authorized representative.\n\n### 5. **Pay the Fees**\n   - Pay the transcript fee as per the university\u2019s guidelines. This can usually be done via Demand Draft (DD), online payment, or at the university cash counter.\n   - Keep the receipt or payment confirmation for future reference.\n\n### 6. **Wait for Processing**\n   - The university will process your request, which may take a few weeks. You will be notified once the transcripts are ready.\n\n### 7. **Collect Your Transcripts**\n   - You can collect the transcripts in person from the university office or request them to be mailed to your address (if this service is available).\n\n### 8. **Contact University Authorities**\n   - If you face any issues or need clarification, contact the **Examination Section** or **Controller of Examinations** at Jadavpur University.\n   - Email: [examinations@jadavpuruniversity.in](mailto:examinations@jadavpuruniversity.in) or [coe@jadavpuruniversity.in](mailto:coe@jadavpuruniversity.in).\n   - Phone: +91-33-2457-2227.\n\n### 9. **For Alumni or Distance Applicants**\n   - If you are an alumni or living outside Kolkata, check if the university provides an online application process or allows authorized representatives to collect documents on your behalf.\n\nMake sure to confirm the exact process and requirements directly with Jadavpur University, as procedures may vary or change over time.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
